{"sections":[],"metadata":{"fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSBulletList","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents14OUDSBulletListV","title":"OUDSBulletList","symbolKind":"struct","roleHeading":"Structure","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"Components"}],"platforms":[{"unavailable":false,"deprecated":false,"name":"iOS","introducedAt":"15.0","beta":false},{"unavailable":false,"deprecated":false,"name":"macOS","introducedAt":"13.0","beta":false},{"unavailable":false,"deprecated":false,"name":"tvOS","introducedAt":"16.0","beta":false},{"unavailable":false,"deprecated":false,"name":"visionOS","introducedAt":"1.0","beta":false},{"unavailable":false,"deprecated":false,"name":"watchOS","introducedAt":"11.0","beta":false}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSBulletList","kind":"identifier"}]},"relationshipsSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s16SendableMetatypeP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"],"kind":"relationships","title":"Conforms To","type":"conformsTo"}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSBulletList"},"kind":"symbol","topicSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSBulletList\/Item"],"title":"Structures","generated":true,"anchor":"Structures"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSBulletList\/init(type:textStyle:isBold:items:)"],"title":"Initializers","generated":true,"anchor":"Initializers"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSBulletList\/body"],"title":"Instance Properties","generated":true,"anchor":"Instance-Properties"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSBulletList\/UnorderedIcon"],"title":"Type Aliases","generated":true,"anchor":"Type-Aliases"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSBulletList\/TextStyle","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSBulletList\/Type","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSBulletList\/UnorderedAsset"],"title":"Enumerations","generated":true,"anchor":"Enumerations"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSBulletList\/View-Implementations","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSBulletList\/View-Implementations"],"title":"Default Implementations","generated":true,"anchor":"Default-Implementations"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsbulletlist"]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"abstract":[{"text":"Bullet list is a UI element that helps to view in related individual text items grouped together; items usually starting with a number or a bullet.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Bullet list is also known as ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Unordered list","type":"text"}]},{"text":" or ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Ordered list","type":"text"}]},{"text":" and is not an interactive element by default.","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@"},{"kind":"attribute","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","text":"MainActor"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSBulletList"}],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"mentions","mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/ContentDisplay"]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Types","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Types"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Three types are proposed:","type":"text"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Unordered (by default)"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": Collects related items that don’t need to be in a specific order or sequence.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Ordered"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": Collects related items with numeric order or sequence.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Bare"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": An unordered list without any bullets or alphanumeric sequence.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Types can be mixed in list, but must be identical for the same ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSBulletList.NestedLevel","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"text":"Levels","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Levels"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Lists can include nested items to indicate hierarchy or subcategories, with indentation distinguishing each level.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Arrange ordered list items logically, such as ranking by importance, highest to lowest values, or in alphabetical \/ numeric order.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Three levels are maximum.","type":"text"}]},{"text":"Text Style","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Text-Style"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"List can be used with different font sizes:","type":"text"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Body Large"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": If the text accompanying the list component is the Body Large text. This variant is designed for more visual, engaging experiences.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Body Medium"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": If the text accompanying the list component is the Body Medium text. This variant is best suited for functional, task-oriented experiences.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"text":"Cases forbidden by design","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Cases-forbidden-by-design"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"it is not allowed to have a depth of items greater than 3","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"}]},{"text":"Internationalisation considerations","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Internationalisation-considerations"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"For latin-based speaking countries, like France, Spain, United Kingdom or Belgium, the european “arabic” numbers are used for the first level of depth","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"of the ordered bullet list. For the second and third levels, the european alphabets are used with upper and lower case values.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"However for countries speaking arabic, these rules can’t be applied. Indeed, there is no notion of upper and lower case characters in arabic alphabet.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"In addition, the numbers in use (i.e. the european “arabic” numbers like “1, 2, 3”) are accepted in arabic countries, even if the “true arabic” numbers (like “ ٢ ٣ ١”) are used","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"in middle-east arabic countries and for official documents.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Thus the OUDS ordered bullet list will use “european” numbers for first level, and arabic alphabets for second and third levels.","type":"text"}]},{"text":"Code samples","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Code-samples"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["       \/\/ 1. Unordered list with bullets","       OUDSBulletList {","           OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 1\")","           OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 2\")","           OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 3\")","       }","","       \/\/ 1.1. Item of Unordered list with bullet as tick, a text style","       \/\/ body medium and text bold","       OUDSBulletList(type: .unordered(asset: .tick),","                      textStyle: .bodyMedium,","                      isBold: true)  {","           OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 1\")","           OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 2\")","           OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 3\")","       }","","       \/\/ 2. Bare list with 3 items","       OUDSBulletList(type: .bare) {","           OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 1\")","           OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 2\")","           OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 3\")","       }","","       \/\/ 3. Ordered list with 3 items","       OUDSBulletList(type: .ordered) {","           OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 1\")","           OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 2\")","           OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 3\")","       }","","       \/\/ 3.1. Ordered list with 3 items in first level,","       \/\/ and one item as sub item (second level),","       \/\/ and 2 items as sub item in (third level)","       OUDSBulletList(type: .ordered) {","           OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 1\") {","               OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 1.1\") {","                   OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 1.1.1\")","                   OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 1.1.2\")","               }","           }","           OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 2\")","           OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 3\")","       }","","       \/\/ Same Bullet list but items in third level with free icon as bullet","       let icon = Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\")","       OUDSBulletList(type: .ordered) {","           OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 1\") {","               OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 1.1\", subListType: .unordered(asset: .icon(icon))) {","                   OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 1.1.1\")","                   OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 1.1.2\")","               }","           }","           OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 2\")","           OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 3\")","       }"],"syntax":"swift"},{"text":"Design documentation","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Design-documentation"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/r.orange.fr\/r\/S-ouds-doc-bullet-list"}]},{"text":"Themes rendering","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Themes-rendering"},{"text":"Orange","type":"heading","level":3,"anchor":"Orange"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_bullet_list_Orange"}]},{"text":"Orange Compact","type":"heading","level":3,"anchor":"Orange-Compact"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_bullet_list_OrangeCompact"}]},{"text":"Sosh","type":"heading","level":3,"anchor":"Sosh"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_bullet_list_Sosh"}]},{"text":"Wireframe","type":"heading","level":3,"anchor":"Wireframe"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_bullet_list_Wireframe"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"1.0.0 (Figma component design version)","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"style":"note","name":"Version","type":"aside"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"1.2.0","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"style":"note","name":"Since","type":"aside"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"references":{"doc://OUDSComponents/7SwiftUI4ViewP":{"type":"unresolvable","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP","title":"SwiftUICore.View"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSBulletList/Type":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"Type"}],"type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"enum"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"Type"}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsbulletlist\/type","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"The visual type of the list","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSBulletList\